					<div class="line" id="">
	    <span class="emphasis">More easily.</span>
	  </div>
					<div class="line" id="">
	    <span class="emphasis">But I&rsquo;ve already</span>
	  </div>
					<div class="line" id="">
	    <span class="emphasis">Learned to walk,</span>
